title: Nike Men's or Women's MetCon 3 Training Shoe (various colors) $76 + Free Shipping
text: Original Post Edited Today at 09:48 AM by annie930ny Road Runner Sports has select colors of the Nike Metcon 3 Men's and Women's on sale for $109.95. The coupon code C7Z1P508 takes $25 off your purchase. In your cart you can add the Road Runner Sports VIP membership for $1.99 and it takes 10% off your order. You must add it by clicking "Get This Price'. You must cancel this membership, otherwise there will be an annual reoccurring charge of $27.99. You can call to cancel after you receive your purchase. My total came to $75.95 with free shipping and no tax for my state.
